The duo explores global influences and contemporary club aesthetics, crafting music that balances technical precision with emotional impact. Maintaining full anonymity, KRAFT CLOUD removes the artist from the spotlight, allowing the audience to engage solely with the experience.`,links:{beatport:"https://www.beatport.com/pt/artist/kraft-cloud/1253425",spotify:"https://open.spotify.com/intl-pt/artist/0HPfjQYmUDRiyGun8HTQP5?si=MdECvOrfTkWfcbb4ggZx9A"}},{id:"child-at-klub",name:"CHILD AT KLUB",imageBW:cj,imageColor:uj,description:`CHILD AT KLUB is the latest musical project by DJ and producer Beher. Drawing from disco, soul funk, Dance Underground, and Progressive House, the project represents a new creative phase focused on innovation and emotional depth.

With a solid trajectory marked by multiple Beatport Top 100 releases across genres such as Deep House, Indie Dance/Nu-Disco, Brazilian Bass, and Tech House, Beher now introduces Subversive House — a sound that merges groove, texture, and hypnotic progression.

CHILD AT KLUB transforms dance floors into immersive experiences, bridging past and future through rhythm, identity, and refined musical storytelling.`,links:{beatport:"https://www.beatport.com/pt/artist/child-at-klub/1189302",spotify:"https://open.spotify.com/intl-pt/artist/2MH32qe8ggqb0ypUx5KU6E?si=gIwvBfioTTy6QtxHwNr-NA"}},{id:"slim-cat",name:"SLIM CAT",imageBW:dj,imageColor:hj,description:`Slim Cat was created with the purpose of merging the plastic precision of Techno with the lightness and groove of House music. Focused on Tech House, the project explores rhythmic contrast, texture, and minimal expression to deliver a distinctive sonic identity.

Anonymity is a core element of Slim Cat's concept. By maintaining a strictly concealed identity across performances and digital platforms, the project cultivates mystery and shifts full attention to the music itself. This approach transforms each release into a conceptual experience driven purely by sound.`,links:{beatport:"https://www.beatport.com/pt/artist/slim-cat/724599",spotify:"https://open.spotify.com/intl-pt/artist/0CWlDMWJxIEzBSdYPJL7Ug?si=i7i6it_eQuKalUi1OxLDhw"}}],vj=[{name:"Paper Street",image:fj},{name:"Synth Soul Pop",image:pj},{name:"TimeWarpX",image:mj}],yj=()=>{const[e,t]=w.useState(null),[r,n]=w.useState(null);return c.jsxs(Et,{children:[c.jsx("div",{className:"fixed top-24 left-6 lg:left-12 z-40",children:c.jsx(kr,{})}),c.jsx(kh,{label:`DJS. 


